-- Suedzucker Forecasts Company's Full-Year Operating Profit, Sales Will Rise
-- Zoe Schneeweiss
-- 2010-09-20T08:51:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/suedzucker-forecasts-company-s-full-year-operating-profit-sales-will-rise.html

          
          
             Suedzucker AG said it expects full-
year operating profit to increase to more than 450 million euros
from 403 million euros last year.  
 The company also said that it expects full-year revenues to
increase to about 5.8 billion euros from 5.7 billion euros last
year.  
 “The boost in earnings will be driven predominantly by the
segments sugar and CropEnergies,” the company said in a
statement today.  
          
          


  


        